{"tid":1173501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深水埗變90年代東莞街 髮廊失控暗格服務老少尋歡","createTime":"2019-05-27T07:05:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T11:20:01.000Z","uid":24044,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"81004ccbdbbf75c8285ffcd27bb5c01b0f4dc648","tid":1173501,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T07:05:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20190527/large/1558939632_3ce8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20190527%2Flarge%2F1558939632_3ce8.jpg&h=870aa05d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_672028_0?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1KeJEEaw0kXAle_7wknAy1ICRW0NYm4n1FdhPPuTtdDBb55Agmwq1z72I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_672028_0%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1KeJEEaw0kXAle_7wknAy1ICRW0NYm4n1FdhPPuTtdDBb55Agmwq1z72I&d=I3HUAc%2BVzuGSjYFa2O0dWPtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=dde962f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_672028_0%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1KeJEEaw0kXAle_7wknAy1ICRW0NYm4n1FdhPPuTtdDBb55Agmwq1z72I&h=3306fabf\" target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_672028_0?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1KeJEEaw0kXAle_7wknAy1ICRW0NYm4n1FdhPPuTtdDBb55Agmwq1z72I</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港愈來愈大陸化，連情色行業也一樣&hellip;&hellip;</span><br />\n<br />\n深水埗這個舊區，一向都有由新移民女子經營的髮廊，她們會暗中提供色情按摩服務，「啲髮廊好奇怪，好似以前國內嘅色情髮廊，但係我唔知裡面係咪色情，因為見到好多中年女性穿著性感短裙，坐喺舖頭裡面。」深水埗街坊阿文說。<br />\n<br />\n近半年來，這些色情髮廊愈開愈多，單是醫局街和海壇街，便有二十多間，再加上附近一帶，保守估計超過四十間，十分誇張，「髮廊啲女人有時都會企喺門口，佢哋多數會兜搭男街坊，問對方入唔入去按摩或者洗頭，而女性則從來無見過有兜搭。」<br />\n<br />\n阿文表示，這些髮廊對附近街坊或多或少都會有影響，「因為有時候自己一個男人路過，佢哋都會走出嚟問你係咪按摩？其實都頗尷尬，又見過有啲女街坊拖住小朋友，行過嗰啲髮廊門口，都唔會行咁埋，盡量離遠少少。最慘係，會吸引好多嫖客來這裡，的確會令環境變得複雜。」<br />\n<br />\n深水埗區議員衞煥南亦說，這類髮廊近一年好像多了，「如果沒記錯，有些鋪頭結業後，就開了這些髮廊。近來我都發現，有街坊投訴，這陣子這些坐在髮廊的女子，因為是隔著玻璃，途人行過時，包括我自己，不知為何會拋媚弄眼，或者叫人入去，現在就是這樣。」他說早前已去信警方，要求加強巡邏。<br />\n<br />\n採訪：專題組"},{"pid":"8b481ad5656f177c1ad608ddb7e9dd9192c92717","tid":1173501,"uid":24044,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T07:07:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/61032970_1069589896583385_4856377048379162624_o.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-2.xx&amp;oh=9fde44d7f6e310733800fb38edd3109a&amp;oe=5D936EDC\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F61032970_1069589896583385_4856377048379162624_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-2.xx%26oh%3D9fde44d7f6e310733800fb38edd3109a%26oe%3D5D936EDC&h=dc68687d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"397416e37720bb3b9c36232cb9c6a7b620881a58","tid":1173501,"uid":76115,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T07:09:52.000Z","msg":"中間more"},{"pid":"298615741927accf323827e7045ebab8777604da","tid":1173501,"uid":207702,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T07:09:59.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 條女咁撚肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74eac89dde2e643f594125307d85d378dd0b6d81","tid":1173501,"uid":210522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b481ad5656f177c1ad608ddb7e9dd9192c92717","tid":1173501,"uid":24044,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T07:07:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/61032970_1069589896583385_48